These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, begonia, iris
There 4 different types of food: onion, cranberry, artichoke, apple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, lacrosse, swimming
4 different games are played: snooker, billiard, scrabble, whist
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating apple##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsiris##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
9. the person who growslily is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | lily | iris   | orchid  | begonia  |
| Food   | cranberry    | apple    | onion      | artichoke    |
| Sport   | swimming | weightlifting | lacrosse | volleyball |
| Game     | whist  | snooker       | billiard    | scrabble     |

