.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, mirinda, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, taxi, airplane
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, architect, writer, software-developer
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, peas, plum, spinach
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
3. the software-developer is the person eating peas##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person driving the airplane is between the writer and the person eating blueberry##2
6. the person eating spinach is between the person driving the airplane and the software-developer##2
7. the nurse is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | cola    | mirinda  | juice    |
| Transport   | snowmobile      | boat  | airplane  | taxi |
| Job           | software-developer      | writer       | architect      | nurse       |
| Food         | peas    | spinach | plum | blueberry |

