6. the bongani-smoker is the craftsman house##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is between the palace house and the craftsman house##2
9. the cape-cod house is between the person who growssunflower and the bongani-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
