 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the australian##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the italian##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the australian is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
10. the indonesian is between the person drinking soy-milk and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Nationality           | australian  | russian | indonesian     | italian |
| Birthday   | august | june  | july | november       |
| Beverage           | lemonade       | tea    | fanta      | soy-milk           |
| City         | hannover | colone   | london   | san-francisco         |

