 4. the fan folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the turkish##1
 7. the fan d&b is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the fan ambient is the russian##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's birthday is in october and the italian##2
10. the indian is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | mouse         | chinchilla         | snake     | goldfish      |
