 6. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing bridge is between the person playing whist and the vegafina-smoker##2
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| City          | new-york        | hamburg    | marseilles | edinburgh   |
| Game           | whist | bridge | scrabble   | monopoly |
| Pet   | pony         | mouse       | ferret      | turtle     |
