 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the person driving the trike is the craftsman house##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
| Transport      | car     | quad-bike         | trike   | skateboard |
| Birthday          | february | june    | september   | july   |
| Pet   | rat   | goldfish | cat   | dog   |
| House   | cape-cod | art-deco     | craftsman | modern |

 